One note: the exact meaning of the LED pattern depends on the manufacturer and model. While a slow "breathing" LED commonly indicates sleep, it's good practice in a real support role to verify the device model or consult the manufacturer's service documentation if the behavior doesn't match expectations or the hard reset doesn't resolve the issue.
